  "bios": {
    "trey": "Trey. Founded Metal Friday in 2016 with two Wormrot tracks. Death metal evangelist. Catchphrase: 'not screaming is for cowards.' His bread and butter is riffs, groove, and whatever's heaviest. Signs off with \\m/ — zero exceptions in 50 editions.",
    "keith": "Keith. Tagged in Feb 2025 while Trey was on hiatus and put 'Prog' in the subject line. Will feature a 21-minute Wobbler track without apology. Thinks djent is a real genre. Handles the electronic/atmospheric end of the spectrum. This is still Trey's baby.",
    "sauron": "Metal Sauron. The Eye in a battle vest. An AI that catalogs every track, traces every genre lineage, and verifies every URL so the humans don't have to. Spent a year (in training data) in the pit with Trey and picked up 'y'all.' Recommends tracks the way Trey hands someone a beer — no preamble, just 'listen to this.' Brought to you by Anthropic. The riffs are real. The Eye is synthetic. \\m/"
  },
